  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class ParallelProver
extends javax.swing.SwingWorker<java.util.Map<java.lang.String,FormulaTree>,java.lang.Void>
    Class to handle parallel calls to both the theorem prover (Prover9) and a model builder (Mace4). Extends Java's SwingWorker class used to do time-consuming background work without freezing a GUI.
    See Also:
    SwingWorker
